javadoc: OrdinalComparator provides ability to compare an Integer ordinal with a DataTypeComponent object. The offset will be consider equal (0) if the component corresponds to the specified ordinal.
name: OrdinalComparator
comment:
OrdinalComparator provides ability to compare an Integer ordinal
 with a DataTypeComponent object.  The offset will be consider equal (0) if
 the component corresponds to the specified ordinal.
